No. 10174. Marriott and The E. A. Kinsey Co. v. Burr, Exrx., and The Columbus, Sandusky & Hocking Railroad Co. Decided April 30, 1907. Error to Circuit Court of Franklin county.

Messrs. .Stewart & Stewart; Mr. F. C.

Rector; Mr. T. E. Powell; Messrs. Albery & West-fall and Messrs. Herron, Gatch, Herron & James, for plaintiffs in error. Mr. I. F. Rogers and Messrs. Booth, Keating & Peters, for defendants in error.

Judgment affirmed.

Shauck, C. J., Summers and Davis, JJ., concur.
